snippet.title: Thirty Flights of Loving
snippet.description:
Explore the world of Thirty Flights of Loving through a first-person short story. In this sequel to Gravity Bone, take a deep dive with high-flying schemers, lovelorn criminals, and more alleycats than you can shake a stick at. http://blendogames.com

This trailer video was made by the fine folks at http://idlethumbs.net
